<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-block_role">Role: Discovery, UX, UI Design</p>
    <p class="text-block_copy">Infor Ming.le is the centralized space for collaboration, business process improvement, and contextual analytics. Fully embedded within ERP, financials, and other organizational systems, this platform enables single-sign on for all Infor CloudSuiteâ„¢ solutions. My task was to create a responsive web experience for the Ming.le shell that encompasses the entire Infor experience. This include the app switcher, share functionality, search and user settings and bookmarks.</p>
</section>

