<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Challenge</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">My challenge was to create a seamless experience for our users across all devices. All of our products are already responsive or in the process of being designed for responsive, so the wrapper that holds them all needed to match. Things I focused on were designing for scale - whether a user had 100 applications or only 1 and optimize core functinalitlies for touch on smaller devices.</p>
</section>

